296
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:42,440
Of course.

297
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:44,240
What about you?

298
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,320
When can you care about yourself?

299
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:49,080
I...

300
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,310
I'm sorry

301
