637
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:53,710
Right?

638
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:54,880
Sang Yan.

639
00:34:55,150 --> 00:34:56,630
We've been sitting here all afternoon,

640
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:58,000
