642
00:35:00,030 --> 00:35:00,800
I don't drink either.

643
00:35:01,150 --> 00:35:01,760
I'm going to drive.

644
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:03,360
Sang Yan, you're so weird,

645
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:04,550
