706
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:38,960
What?

707
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:39,760
You can't wait?

708
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,960
I'm just curious.

709
00:36:45,070 --> 00:36:46,400
Is this coat really nice?

710
