Of course.

711
00:36:48,070 --> 00:36:48,880
Both the shape

712
00:36:49,360 --> 00:36:50,150
and the fabric.

713
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:51,760
And it's very warm, too.

714
00:36:51,920 --> 00:36:52,760
I'm even sweating.

715
00:36:55,190 --> 00:36:55,920
I was going to say

716
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:57,230
