790
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,440
She always remembers

791
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:19,110
what everyone likes

792
00:40:20,590 --> 00:40:21,670
and our birthdays.

793
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:24,880
